cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.DS, cs.AI, cs.CC

Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper deals with grammatical inference and natural language.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper proposes an extended formulation and efficient algorithms for minimizing non-recursive grammars.
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is relevant as the paper discusses algorithms for solving the Smallest Grammar Problem.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is relevant as the paper deals with machine learning and natural language processing.
- cs.CC (Computational Complexity) is less likely but still possible as the paper discusses the complexity of the problem and the efficiency of the proposed algorithms.
